{"query":"query findEntities(
	$filter: EntityFilterInput
	$sort: JSON
	$pagination: PaginationInput
) {
	findEntities(filter: $filter, sort: $sort, pagination: $pagination) {
		result {
			id
			logo {
				id
				originalName
				name
				directory
				fullpath
				fullpaths
				directoriesNames
				extension
				type
				title
				description
				active
				createdAt
				updatedAt
				createdBy
				updatedBy
			}
			organigramme {
				id
				originalName
				name
				directory
				fullpath
				fullpaths
				directoriesNames
				extension
				type
				title
				description
				active
				createdAt
				updatedAt
				createdBy
				updatedBy
			}
			label
			colorGradiantLeft
			colorGradiantRight
			colorHeader
			colorSticker
			description
			linkedin
			totalEmployees
			creationDate
			active
			createdAt
			updatedAt
			deletedAt
		}

		pagination {
			page
			totalPage
			total
			hasNext
			hasPrevious
			limit
		}
	}
}
","operationName":"findEntities","variables":{"filter":{},"sort":{"label":"ASC"},"pagination":{}}}

{"query":"query findAllEmployees(
	$filter: EmployeeFilterInput

}
","operationName":"findAllEmployees","variables":{"filter":{},"pagination":{"limit":10,"page":1}}}
